data.meta_description: When Dan + Shay brings the Heartbreak on the Map Summer Tour to Bangor on Aug. 11, we want our loyal listeners to be there.
data.text:
When Dan + Shay brings the Heartbreak on the Map Summer Tour to Bangor on Aug. 11, we want our loyal listeners to be there.

Dan + Shay will also bring Jake Owen and Dylan Marlowe to the Maine Savings Amphitheater stage. It will be a great show and, best of all, you don't have to miss it!

Here's what to do. Enter your information below. Then, watch for a call from our Q106.5 Morning Show dynamic duo David and Cindy. Put our studio line (207-991-9500) in your phone so you know it's us.

IMPORTANT: Be sure to answer if we call. If not, we move on to another listener.

Now that you've entered your info, good luck!
